   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>When the power is turned on, press and hold the buttons more 3 seconds at the same
        time as below; </p>
            <p>
               <ul>
                  <li>U.S.A: Hold down <image href="media/image380.png" placement="inline"/> and press <image href="media/image381.png" placement="inline"/> more 3 seconds</li>
               </ul>
               <p>FM: 87.7 - 107.9 MHz (200 kHz step)</p>
               <p>AM: 530 - 1.7 10 kHz (10kHz step)</p>
               <ul>
                  <li>South America: Hold down <image href="media/image382.png" placement="inline"/> and press <image href="media/image383(1).png" placement="inline"/> more 3 seconds<p>FM: 87.5 - 108.0 MHz (100 kHz step)</p>
                     <p>AM: 530 - 1.7 10 kHz (10kHz step)</p>
                  </li>
                  <li>Asia: Hold down <image href="media/image380(1).png" placement="inline"/> and press <image href="media/image383(1).png" placement="inline"/> more 3 seconds<p>FM: 87.5 - 108.0 MHz (100 kHz step)</p>
                     <p>AM: 531 - 1,602 kHz (9 kHz step)</p>
                  </li>
                  <li>Europe: Hold down <image href="media/image382(1).png" placement="inline"/> and press <image href="media/image381(1).png" placement="inline"/> seconds<p>FM: 87.5 - 108.0 MHz (50 kHz step)</p>
                     <p>AM: 522 - 1,629 kHz (9 kHz step)</p>
                  </li>
               </ul>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Please wait for more 5 seconds with no operation, the unit will save and apply
        your's setting.</p>
            <p>
               <p>If the region setting is not selected correctly to your country or region,
          the radio reception can not be received. Retry the setting the region of radio reception
          correctly.</p>
               <p>The region setting is required only for the first time</p>
               <p>The region
          setting is return to the default setting when the power connector or battery is
          disconnected.</p>
            </p>
         </li>
      </ol>
